## Task 2: Clean Text Fields

The following fields were cleaned and standardized:

- customer_name
- segment
- region
- state
- city
- category
- sub_category
- ship_mode
- payment_status
- order_status

Cleaning performed:
- Removed leading and trailing spaces using TRIM()
- Removed extra spaces between words
- Standardized capitalization using PROPER()
- Removed unwanted special characters using SUBSTITUTE()
- Standardized inconsistent category and status values using Find & Replace and Flash Fill

Result:
All text fields were converted into a consistent and analysis-ready format.
